#Key concepts
1)High Availability - Ability to keep the service is up and running for long period of time.
Make sure very little down time for bussines.
2)Scalability - ability to increase/decrease resouces for given workload.
3)Elasticity - ability to automatically or dynamically increase or decrease the resource as needed.
4)Agility - ability to react quickly.Cloud services can allocate and deallocate resources quickly.
5)Fault tolerance - one component is failed backup component takes its place.
6)Disaster Recovery - Ability to recover from an event which is taken down a cloud service climate services disaster revoery can recovery very quickly,
with automation and services being readily available to you global reach.
